Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 燙 好燙燙燙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等～啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間她說「請吃吧」 還一臉自滿的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得好像有些寒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因為波波個頭最大 所以給你最大的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說「因為波波個頭最大」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我確實變成大塊頭了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 真好吃啊 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會給我一個最什麼的呢？芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…雪集的話 是加葡萄乾最多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒那麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要你直接告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙…紙 筆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這樣就可以知道芽間的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？寫不出來啦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 日記本上都可以寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 還有墨水的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來 再給我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子 好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺 這會兒好困
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像力氣都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 沒生我們的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她原諒我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有原諒 現在還不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…生氣的話 是不會…給我們做蒸麵包的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為不原諒 才出現來折磨我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能寫字的話 當初就寫字給我們看多好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做的話 又能對話 又能讓大家很快相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳也是 芽間也是 都少根筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說要我們相信芽間的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是想一個人獨佔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的錢好好存著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把煙花做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要讓芽間成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮成那樣 當然會很累啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 正打算一起做煙花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…讓你成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你…你醒著…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就…夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉圈圈～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 跑太快危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.21,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 芽間在跑嗎 那我也來～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.79,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這邊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.25,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}等等 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法…沒法原諒喜歡仁碳的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不能…放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周的排班 能不能和我稍微換一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排班？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期四橋那邊要施工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為日薪很高 所以想去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 總算跑夠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.45,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}喂 喂 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 對面有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子的媽媽 和山先生聯繫過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…叔叔不反對煙花的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還活在過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子發生了那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以來時間就靜止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把她拉回現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不想讓她再想起那些事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松雪君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想冒昧地說 我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的女兒…芽衣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡她！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想為芽衣子做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…我也一直活在過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然做出那麼遜的事 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒變呢 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了芽間 什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎 讓芽間成佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼執著於芽間的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且通過宿海都可以和她說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要通過宿海呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海 現在去打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天也會很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算先送芽間回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…在那兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她啊 說不想悶在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪兒都跟著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我想跟大家一起努力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是「想和大家在一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮還很長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說 跟我們一樣長大了呢 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會喜歡這種醜八怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多…算是…漂…亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說 算可愛…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫算是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳是笨笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.12,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}笨蛋 呆茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吵啊 笨蛋 你就勉強算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在看獨角戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 應該不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集壞掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.06,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(861,261)}第九集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.06,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(755,326)}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.06,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(750,392)}和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.06,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(750,458)}芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 給你們做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花～煙花～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:34.22,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}成了成了成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能讓你們碰火藥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要不要幫我 做些簡單的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 成功啦 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 嚇死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這個會從竹筒裡飛出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得多些紅色會更可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你給人的印象還真不一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在這裡點火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這邊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個只是裝飾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了爬發射台的時候好拿才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.39,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 這邊也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 那樣很危險的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放手啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 做好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在跳到你背上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:52.74,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}波波波波 波波～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看不見…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 比不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前比不上 現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比不過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我去買點兒果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你逃出來 我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快喊出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間在旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻…看不見芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和芽間再見一次面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼只有宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是非宿海不可的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海也 果然是非芽間不可的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和那時候一樣 什麼都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表白失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明喊出了仁碳 卻馬上變成宿海了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊！你那種把人看穿了一樣的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看穿的也只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是相似人之間才有的共鳴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你這種品質惡劣的人相似
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 冷靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說過的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的那句 「我們 要不要交往看看」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 還真是對男生沒抗性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 nice middle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.27,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：nice middle:帥氣深思的中年男性，女性是nice midi；\N另意為格鬥時漂亮的中段踢，此處為後者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼nice middle啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嚇到我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麽嚇人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我燃起來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴的布娃娃不在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 突然就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像個變化無常的小貓 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如果 芽間真的在仁碳那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現了願望 芽間不就消失了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 打工的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 你怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和波波在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是想待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好待吧 待個夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太瘋了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我高興嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…很高興吧 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:45.64,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}對了 那個我看了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.30,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季校服…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}女高中生使雙截棍打的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:50.22,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊 你總算看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為…她是夏天的猛獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:59.18,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}…我還買那個的DVD了 裡面說要出新作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:00.42,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}新作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經開始穿冬季校服了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:03.84,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}…女孩在香港和殭屍戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 寫上去了～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.50,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,354)}你好。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 好厲害啊 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…但是家裡的便簽就寫不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多寫些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多說些話吧
