Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候…那個…我…
